com.shwy.bestjoy.contacts.backup.pim.vcard

类 VCardEntryCommitter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shwy.bestjoy.contacts.backup.pim.vcard.VCardEntryCommitter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    VCardEntryHandler

    public class VCardEntryCommitter
extends java.lang.Object
implements VCardEntryHandler

    VCardEntryHandler implementation which commits the entry to ContentResolver.

    Note:
    Each vCard may contain big photo images encoded by BASE64, If we store all vCard entries in memory, OutOfMemoryError may be thrown. Thus, this class push each VCard entry into ContentResolver immediately.
